  "title": "National Australia Bank deploys AI analytics tools",
  "full_text": "National Australia Bank (NAB: ASX) has announced the launch of artificial intelligence (AI) tools.\nThe firm has announced the launch of conversational AI analytics tools: Databricks' Genie and Genie code tools.\nThe launch of the tools is intended to make querying complex datasets easier. Genie is claimed to translates plain English business questions into structured query language (SQL) queries.\n[Editorial queries for this story should be sent to gbn@enpublishing.co.uk]\nElectronic News Publishing Ltd.\nDocument GLOBAN0020260622em6m0005t",
